{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came to our house, and he said, I am so-and-so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's my name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have heard that you help people and I'm going to be caught tonight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they are coming to my house and I have nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know that you hide people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Will you please hide me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, well, I-- why-- why should I hide you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, well, I know that you have to play innocent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I know that you are hiding Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, well, I don't know what you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's certainly not the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, well, I talked for about half an hour for him before I finally got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two or three nights later, I was-- my husband and I had to go out a moment, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes it was crazy with all those people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- all the Jewish people didn't even like each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And women would fight, and all-- it was a difficult situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one night I said to my husband, let's get out and have a cup of coffee-- which they called coffee, there was no real coffee anymore-- and so we went to this bar, of-- or, restaurant, and or that coffee-- some brown stuff that they called coffee-- and I saw, in another table, I saw there that man who had tried to hide with me, with a group of Jewish-- of German soldiers-- officers.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, I ran away from there, when I was-- I didn't want to see him and I didn't want him to see me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then I knew that I had done the right thing, that he was a traitor.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
